import React from 'react'

import { Grid, Segment } from 'semantic-ui-react'
import '../stylesheets/userConsole.css'


const Fight = (props) => { 
	return(
		<Grid id='fightgrid' columns='equal'>

			<Grid.Column>
				<Segment>1</Segment>
				<Segment>2</Segment>
			</Grid.Column>
			
			<Grid.Column>
				<Segment>1</Segment>
				<Segment>2</Segment>
			</Grid.Column>
			</Grid.Row>
		</Grid>
	)
}

export default Fight;
